Start
Display "Enter a number (1-12) to get the corresponding month:"
Read MonthNumber
Set MonthName to "Invalid"
If MonthNumber equals 1 then:Set MonthName to "January"
Else if MonthNum equals 2 then:Set MonthName to "February"
Else if MonthNum equals 3 then:Set MonthName to "March"
Else if MonthNum equals 4 then:Set MonthName to "April"
Else if MonthNum equals 5 then:Set MonthName to "May"
Else if MonthNum equals 6 then:Set MonthName to "June"
Else if MonthNum equals 7 then:Set MonthName to "July"
Else if MonthNum equals 8 then:Set MonthName to "August"
Else if MonthNum equals 9 then:Set MonthName to "September"
Else if MonthNum equals 10 then:Set MonthName to "October"
Else if MonthNum equals 11 then:Set MonthName to "November"
Else if MonthNum equals 12 then:Set MonthName to "December"
If MonthName equals "Invalid" then:
Display " Re-Enter a valid Number."
Else:
Display "The month is: ", MonthName
End if
End
